OL,3,CPensioners in NI will receive winter
OL,4,Cfuel payment
OL,6,FPensioners in Northern Ireland will
OL,7,Freceive their winter fuel payment this
OL,8,Fyear, Communities Minister Gordon
OL,9,FLyons has said.
OL,11,FIn a statement to the Assembly, Mr
OL,12,FLyons said he had engaged with
OL,13,FExecutive colleagues to reinstate the
OL,14,Fpayment in Northern Ireland and the
OL,15,Fnecessary legislation would be in
OL,16,Fplace by the end of July.
