OL,6,FOn Monday, Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,7,Fannounced a major U-turn on the
OL,8,Fdecision to scrap the winter fuel
OL,9,Fpayment for all but the poorest
OL,10,Fpensioners.
OL,12,FShe said nine million pensioners in
OL,13,FEngland and Wales will now be in
OL,14,Freceipt of the payment this year,
OL,15,Ffollowing an intense backlash since
OL,16,Fthe initial decision to cut the
OL,17,Fbenefit.
