OL,3,CPensioners in NI will receive winter
OL,4,Cfuel payment
OL,6,FPensioners on an income of, or below,
OL,7,F#35,000 will be entitled to the
OL,8,Fpayment of #200 ` rising to #300 for
OL,9,Fthe over-80s ` although a payment will
OL,10,Fbe made to all pensioners. Those not
OL,11,Feligible have the option to opt out of
OL,12,Fthe payment or will have the payment
OL,13,Frecovered through HMRC.
OL,15,FMr Lyons had previously said he needed
OL,16,Ffurther clarity on what the
OL,17,Fannouncement meant for Northern
OL,18,FIreland.
