OL,6,FHe said: "Since yesterday's
OL,7,Fannouncement my officials have been
OL,8,Fengaging with officials in the
OL,9,FDepartment for Work and Pensions (DWP)
OL,10,Fto understand the impact for Northern
OL,11,FIreland. I also met with Torsten Bell
OL,12,FMP, Parliamentary Secretary (HM
OL,13,FTreasury) and Parliamentary Under-
OL,14,FSecretary (DWP) along with the Finance
OL,15,FMinister John O'Dowd.
OL,17,F"Today I have engaged with Executive
OL,18,Fministers on the re-instatement of the
OL,19,FWinter Fuel Payment in Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
