OL,4,Cfuel payment
OL,6,F"My officials are continuing to work
OL,7,Fwith DWP and HMRC officials to
OL,8,Fdetermine the number of NI pensioners
OL,9,Fimpacted by this announcement,
OL,10,Fparticularly the number of pensioners
OL,11,Fwho exceed the #35,000 threshold."
OL,13,FAfter the UK Government restricted
OL,14,Feligibility for winter fuel payments
OL,15,Flast year, Mr Lyons announced a one-
OL,16,Foff #100 payment to pensioner
OL,17,Fhouseholds affected.
