OL,6,FThe minister added: "Almost 250,000
OL,7,Fpayments were issued, as promised, to
OL,8,Fmost Northern Ireland pensioners by
OL,9,Fthe end of March 2025.
OL,11,F"While this one-off payment helped to
OL,12,Fsupport pensioners last winter, I know
OL,13,Fthat many of them remained anxious and
OL,14,Fworried about their energy bills this
OL,15,Fwinter and beyond.
OL,17,F"I therefore welcome Treasury's
OL,18,Fannouncement yesterday to reinstate
OL,19,Fthe Winter Fuel Payment to everyone
OL,20,Fover State Pension age with an income
OL,21,Fof, or below, #35,000 a year.
